<TITLE>Gump&emdash;A Front-End Generator for Oz</TITLE>
<AUTHOR
        INFO="WWW=http://www.ps.uni-sb.de/~kornstae/"
>Leif Kornstaedt</AUTHOR>
<ABSTRACT>
<P>
        This manual describes <Q/Gump/, the front-end generator for Oz.
        It reads Oz files with embedded scanner and&slash;or parser definitions
        and produces Oz files as output where these have been replaced by
        classes implementing scanners and&slash;or parsers.  The semantic
        actions in the specifications allow the full flexibility and
        expressivity of Oz to be used.
</ABSTRACT>
